quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  39,68,"The Trumpet will be blown and all those in the heavens and all those on the earth will fall dead, except those God wills ňĻto spareňļ. Then it will be blown again and they will rise up at once, looking on ňĻin anticipationňļ"
